description: Our Shaved Ice Delights™ are simply irresistible. We find that people of all ages come together and share unique moments while enjoying our huge mouth-watering delights!Snow Caps Shaved Ice Delights™ is here to stay!! Our HUGE mouth watering Delights are a hit on the streets. We find that people of all ages come together to share unique brain freeze moments while enjoying our life size Caps.Mouth watering flavors: Strawberry, Wild Cherry, Blue Raspberry, Orange Pineapple, Piña Colada, Lemon Lime, Blue Bubble Gum, Green Apple, Grape, Watermelon & Banana.Snow Caps mission is all about family, fun and community events! Now a days our lives are run by dual income households, hectic schedules and virtual worlds. We believe in bringing back family outings. Our community is our playground; get out and share in the fun!
